data.title: Weather in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia data archive for October 29, 2015
data.meta_description: The past weather in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia on October 29, 2015: temperature, wind, precipitation and relative air humidity
data.text:
Borisovka weather at night on October 29, 2015: overcast, no precipitation or weather events have been observed. The atmospheric pressure was normal. Air temperature -1…2°C. Southern gentle 0—10.8 km/h winds. Relative humidity 95—100%.

In the afternoon of October 29, 2015 Borisovka weather was as follows: overcast, mist. The pressure was normal. Air temperature 0…3°C. Southern gentle 10.8—14.4 km/h winds. Relative humidity 89—97%.

On this page you can find out what was the weather in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia on October 29, 2015 according to the observation data of the weather station with the the World Meteorological Organization index 28573.
